<view class="page home-page">
  <view class="brand-bar">
    <view class="brand-mark">⌘</view>
    <text>Join the Fun</text>
    <text class="brand-bell">⌂</text>
  </view>

  <view class="clock-card">
    <view class="clock-top">
      <text>{{currentWeekday}}</text>
      <text class="clock-date">{{currentDate}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="clock-time">{{currentTime}}</view>
    <view class="clock-caption">祝你有美好的一天</view>
  </view>

  <view class="daily-card card card-pad">
    <view class="daily-chip">♥ 每日温柔提醒</view>
    <view class="daily-title">今天也要 对自己好一点</view>
    <view class="daily-desc">在这个快节奏的世界里，别忘了停下来，给自己的心灵一个大大的拥抱。</view>
    <view class="primary-btn daily-action" bindtap="goBustle">开启美好一天</view>
    <image class="daily-image" src="/assets/events/cat.png" mode="aspectFill" />
  </view>

  <view class="hot-card" bindtap="goBustle">
    <view class="hot-icon">
      <view class="hot-icon-core"></view>
    </view>
    <view class="hot-title">本市热门</view>
    <view class="hot-desc">查看大家都在逛哪里</view>
    <view class="hot-arrow">→</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">发现生活中的小确幸</view>
    <view class="home-copy">
      不论是清晨的一杯热茶，还是路边的一朵野花，都是大自然给你的小惊喜。记录下这些瞬间，让美好在心中流淌。
    </view>
    <view class="habit-list">
      <view class="habit-item" wx:for="{{checklist}}" wx:key="*this">
        <text class="habit-check">✓</text>
        <text>{{item}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <image class="landscape-image" src="/assets/events/park.png" mode="aspectFill" />
  </view>

  <view class="card card-pad empty-state" wx:if="{{errorText}}">
    <view class="item-title">今天的推荐暂时没加载出来</view>
    <view class="item-desc">{{errorText}}</view>
  </view>
</view>
